source: crates/wasm-cli/tests/test.rs
expression: output
---
Compose and manage sets of interdependent Wasm components

Usage: wasm compose [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  build    Build a composed component from a WAC script
  plug     Plug component exports into a socket component's imports
  targets  Check if a component conforms to a WIT world
  parse    Parse a WAC file and print its AST as JSON
  resolve  Parse and resolve a WAC file and print the resolved representation as JSON
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version

Global Options:
      --color <WHEN>  When to use colored output [default: auto] [possible values: auto, always, never]
      --offline       Run in offline mode
